:

1. Čuo sam *glasine* da je nova knjiga veoma dobra. (I heard rumors that the new book is very good.)
2. U gradu se šire *glasine* o misterioznom čoveku. (In the town, rumors are spreading about a mysterious man.)
3. Ova izjava je stvorila *glasine* o njegovoj nepoštovanju prema drugima. (This statement created rumors about his disrespect towards others.)
4. Ona je zanemarila *glasine* o njegovoj nevini. (She ignored rumors about his innocence.)
5. Nastavljaju se *glasine* da će se takmičenje održati u sledećem mesecu. (Rumors continue that the competition will be held next month.)